data.description: This elegant single family home sits in the highly desirable Northside Estates, just minutes to the beautiful Legacy Park with a fishing pond, Gazebo's to BBQ, Skate Park, Basketball court & Playground. Upon entrance, you are warmly greeted by a bright and open floor plan seamlessly connecting the kitchen to the living room & leading to the inviting, sunny backyard. Meticulous attention to detail is presented in the kitchen with granite countertops, plenty of cabinet storage, and stainless steel appliances. Adjacent to the formal dining area, there’s a comfortable family room & a bonus bedroom or office space that provide additional flexibility. Upstairs you’ll find 4 more bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. The master bedroom is large with no lack of storage, incl. a separate walk-in closet & custom vanity in the master bath with granite counters & a beautiful tile shower. UPDATES incl.: roof, water heater, flooring, bathrooms, kitchen, blinds, laundry chute, central vacuum system. **Option to assume VA loan at 4.750%**
